snippet.title: Wuthering Waves Official Release Trailer | Waking of a World
snippet.description:
"I'm crashing through the silence, I'm coming with the rising tide"
Pre-register for Wuthering Waves now: https://akioversea.onelink.me/lKVo/7n76bkvu
Wuthering Waves Official Release Trailer: Waking of a World, officially releases now!
Singer: Will Stetson (https://www.youtube.com/@willstetson)
Mix/master: @niu_arx
lyrics: @yayariutai

Wuthering Waves will launch on May 22 (PT) globally across platforms.
Pre-download will begin on May 21 at 03:00 (PT).

✦Follow our official social media for the latest news and updates✦
Official Website: http://wutheringwaves.kurogame.com/en
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WutheringWaves.Official
X/Twitter: https://twitter.com/Wuthering_Waves
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/WutheringWaves
Discord: https://discord.gg/wutheringwaves
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/WutheringWaves
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@wutheringwaves_official
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wuthering_waves

#WutheringWaves #WakingofaWorld
